%% x-task-manager: Task Manager
%% Universal task operations (create/update/replan) with automatic decomposition
%% Decompose-First Pattern: Build IDEAL plan → Check existing → Create or Replan

graph TD
    Start([Start: Task Manager]) --> Phase1[Phase 1: Discovery<br/>Team ID auto-discovery<br/>Parse Story ID from request]

    Phase1 --> Phase2[Phase 2: Analyze & Decompose ALWAYS<br/>Load Story AC + Technical Notes<br/>Build IDEAL task plan 1-6<br/>Consumer-First ordering]

    Phase2 --> Phase3{Phase 3: Check<br/>Existing Tasks?}

    Phase3 -->|Count = 0| CreateMode[CREATE MODE<br/>No existing tasks]
    Phase3 -->|Count ≥ 1| ReplanMode[REPLAN MODE<br/>Compare ideal vs existing]

    CreateMode --> Generate[Generate task documents<br/>7 sections with guide links<br/>from IDEAL plan]
    Generate --> ShowCreate[Show preview:<br/>1-6 tasks to create<br/>Consumer-First order]
    ShowCreate --> ConfirmCreate{User<br/>confirms?}
    ConfirmCreate -->|No| Phase2
    ConfirmCreate -->|Yes| ExecuteCreate[Create all tasks in Linear<br/>Update kanban_board.md]
    ExecuteCreate --> End([End: Summary])

    ReplanMode --> LoadExisting[Load existing task descriptions<br/>Full 7 sections each<br/>Note current status]
    LoadExisting --> Compare[Compare IDEAL plan vs existing<br/>Identify operations needed]
    Compare --> Categorize[Categorize operations:<br/>KEEP UPDATE OBSOLETE CREATE]
    Categorize --> ShowReplan[Show operations summary + diffs<br/>KEEP: no changes<br/>UPDATE: AC/approach changed<br/>OBSOLETE: Cancel state=Canceled<br/>CREATE: new tasks needed]
    ShowReplan --> ConfirmReplan{User<br/>confirms?}
    ConfirmReplan -->|No| Phase2
    ConfirmReplan -->|Yes| ExecuteReplan[Execute operations:<br/>Keep/Update/Cancel/Create in Linear]
    ExecuteReplan --> UpdateKanban[Update kanban_board.md<br/>Remove Canceled tasks<br/>Add new tasks]
    UpdateKanban --> End

    %% Styling
    classDef discovery fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1976D2,stroke-width:2px
    classDef processing fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#F57C00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#FFE0B2,stroke:#E64A19,stroke-width:2px
    classDef action fill:#C8E6C9,stroke:#388E3C,stroke-width:2px

    class Phase1,Phase2,LoadExisting discovery
    class CreateMode,ReplanMode,Generate,Compare,Categorize processing
    class Phase3,ConfirmCreate,ConfirmReplan decision
    class ExecuteCreate,ExecuteReplan,UpdateKanban,End action
